metadata.description: Alien Bois Collective presents the Alien Bois Genesis NFT collection. We are kickstarting a NEW community-driven & supported media platform for UFO enthusiasts, researchers, and scientific experts advocating for disclosure of Intelligent Extraterrestrial Life. Each NFT Owner will receive an All Access pass to the “ecosystem” (ABCS podcasts, streaming content, Live Chats and IRL events and/or conferences soon to be announced.)
